This is the configuration for speed.twistedmatrix.com.

It is adminstered using braid[1]. It is installed in `/srv/codespeed` as user codepseed.
It uses the following directories

~/config - This repository.
~/bin - commands to start and stop the server
~/log - log files
~/run - pid files
~/codespeed - codespeed source
~/data/codespeed.db - database

The following fabric commands are available:

install - Create user and install configuration.
update - Updates the configuration and restarts the server.
dump:<dump> - Dump database to file.
restore:<dump> - Restore database from file.
installTestData - Create an empty database for testing.
start - Start server.
stop - Stop server.
restart - Restart the server.

[1] https://github.com/twisted-infra/braid
